		description: "Get more calls for roofing, pressure washing, landscaping, cleaning, HVAC, and other home services. We optimize for Coronado properties and island-wide searches that drive booked jobs year-round."
	},
	{
		heading: "Med Spas, Salons & Wellness Professionals",
		description: "Stand out in Coronado's upscale wellness market. We target high-intent searches like \"med spa Coronado,\" \"massage near Hotel Del,\" and luxury wellness services that attract affluent clients."
	},
	{
