	},
	{
		question: "How do seasonal patterns affect Coronado SEO?",
		answer: "Coronado's business visibility changes with the seasons ‚Äî tourism peaks, local home projects, and real estate waves all shift search intent. We monitor these changes in real time and optimize around tourism surges, seasonal home services (landscaping, repairs, cleaning, remodeling), and high-value local searches. Our campaigns adapt so you never lose momentum ‚Äî even in the off-season."
